sequenceDiagram
    participant Rider
    participant Driver
    participant API as API de viajes
    participant Location as Location updater
    participant Geo as Geo index
    participant Match as Matching engine
    participant State as Ride state machine
    participant Events as Event log

    Driver->>Location: reportar ubicación
    Location->>Geo: actualizar celda disponible
    Rider->>API: solicitar viaje
    API->>Match: buscar candidatos cercanos
    Match->>Geo: leer celda y vecinas
    Geo-->>Match: drivers disponibles
    Match->>State: asignar driver
    State->>Events: ride assigned
    State-->>API: ride_id + driver_id
    API-->>Rider: viaje asignado
